{"tid":2259090,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日本NEC取代華為 建設英國5G通訊系統","createTime":"2020-10-26T14:02:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-28T09:33:47.000Z","uid":21470,"like":118,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"f5ffac991b8a3d460aed16f7b692fbe663ce99d0","tid":2259090,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T14:02:24.000Z","msg":"日本NEC取代華為 建設英國5G通訊系統<br />\n<br />\n日本傳媒報道，日本電氣(NEC)將取代中國電訊設備製造商華為，在英國建設5G通訊系統。英國國際貿易大臣卓慧思日前到日本，簽署英日經濟夥伴關係協定（EPA），並與NEC董事長遠藤信博會談，磋商建立5G設備地點。<br />\n<br />\n美國政府以國家安全為理由封殺華為，並要求英國在內的盟友，不要採用華為5G產品。英國政府早前決定2027年前排除華為產品。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/international/2363312\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2F2363312&d=PtGeCDSqwX4ndXcvBPlETXyU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=3cc56f97\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/international/2363312</a>"},{"pid":"5e39ed1657c93ea2b2a3c860c5d00ddfaa89e9b9","tid":2259090,"uid":228955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T14:03:52.000Z","msg":"Good"},{"pid":"e11f8974b16baa91ca64cce603804d4528579679","tid":2259090,"uid":312598,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T14:04:06.000Z","msg":"日本貨特別正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"620e92a788a1db11f48ae68eb06b35e61606c2ba","tid":2259090,"uid":231583,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T14:04:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"721e67fea1d1584fd46f575c87ae699822f159a8","tid":2259090,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T14:04:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"692923bc055bd8d177cc6c8d8a45c7dc6000a0af","tid":2259090,"uid":40